item.title: Spartan Workout Tour
item.description:
Spartan Workout Tour

Alpha Obstacle Training hosted the Spartan training tour. After a good warmup, 3 8 minute intervals followed by obstacle training.

item.title: Ice storm made hill repeats tough
item.description:
Ice storm made hill repeats tough

Stepping into new ice or snow makes every step different and difficult. This was a laborious workout. My Icebug DTS2 shoes have made a big difference over my winter training. I've been able to get out more and faster.

item.title: Winter is back
item.description:
Winter is back

Ice storm made monkey bars tricky. Woke up feeling tired in the morning. Felt OK out there. Did some up and over repeats. Burpees at the bottom, rig at the top.

item.title: The only cake I really like
item.description:
The only cake I really like

Coffee cake from my mom. A good cheat :) I haven't talked about nutrition much. At this age, it's actually more than half the battle. My basic approach is eat a light dinner. I have found it helps me sleep better anyways.

item.title: Week 2 Day 2 - Nike Speed Run
item.description:
Week 2 Day 2 - Nike Speed Run

This is a 800m + 3x400m + 400m recovery + 800m + 3x400m + 400m recovery.

item.title: Week 2 Day 1: Warm up heart rate weird
item.description:
Week 2 Day 1: Warm up heart rate weird

I felt like I couldn't push the pace. The good news was that my lungs were good, but felt my legs couldn't extend the stride as much.

item.title: Rock climbing on pull up bar
item.description:
Rock climbing on pull up bar

I was surprised to see this at LA fitness in Burlington. Bonus! Used these for an unstructured core workout after the long run.

item.title: Sulphur Springs Practice
item.description:
Sulphur Springs Practice

I am running a couple of 25KM trail races. I've never run that distance before. So I've made a point to not only practice the distance, but also the trail.

item.title: Steeper 400m Bucket Carry
item.description:
Steeper 400m Bucket Carry

Felt easier than the 1KM carry I do by my house.

item.title: Hill Repeats: 609m elevation gain
item.description:
Hill Repeats: 609m elevation gain

Surprised there's still snow. Felt pretty strong at the end. Had enough for a bucket carry. I should try this loop at a faster pace.
